# Matilda Stokes Portfolio Website

## 📁 File Structure

```
/
├── index.html                      # Homepage
├── granular-synth.html            # Ceramic Granular Synthesiser project page
├── extended-composition.html       # Extended composition project page
├── soundcloud-works.html          # SoundCloud works collection
├── about.html                     # Expanded bio page
├── style.css                      # Styles with subtle glitch effects
├── /img                           # Image folder
│   ├── abstract-1.jpg
│   ├── line-forms.jpg
│   ├── poster-green.jpg
│   └── [your other images]
└── /media                         # Audio files folder
    ├── Introductory-work.mp3
    ├── introductory-work-2.mp3
    └── [your other audio files]
```

## ✏️ What You Need To Add

Search for `<!-- TODO:` in each HTML file. These comments mark everywhere you need to add your content. Here's a breakdown:

### 🏠 index.html
- Update audio files in the "Now playing" section
- Replace placeholder images with your actual project photos
- Add your GitHub URL

### 🎛️ granular-synth.html
- Main hero image of your ceramic synthesiser
- 6 audio demo files (media/granular-demo-1.mp3 through 6)
- Descriptions for each audio demo
- Process/development photos
- Optional: Link to your full dissertation PDF

### 🎵 extended-composition.html
- Project description and context
- Main audio file
- Duration, year, and context information
- Technical details about your composition process
- Relevant images

### 🎧 soundcloud-works.html
- Track titles and audio files
- Track descriptions
- Your SoundCloud profile URL
- You can use either HTML5 audio players OR SoundCloud embed iframes

### 👤 about.html
- Professional headshot photo (img/matilda-photo.jpg)
- Expanded bio text
- Your BA graduation year
- Studio/action photos
- Additional details about your practice

## 🎨 Design Features

### Subtle Glitch Effects
- **Text glitch**: Slight shake on hover (`.glitch-text`)
- **Heading glitch**: RGB split effect that appears on hover (`.glitch-text-hover`)
- **Image distortion**: Subtle contrast/position shift on hover (`.glitch-img`)
- **Noise overlay**: Slight grain texture appears on cards when hovered

### Color Scheme
- Background: Deep black (#000)
- Surface: Dark gray (#111)
- Accent: Pink (#ff4081)
- Secondary: Blue (#3b82f6)

## 📝 Adding Content Examples

### Adding a New Audio Track
```html
<li data-src="media/your-track-name.mp3">Track Title</li>
```

### Adding a Gallery Image
```html
<div class="gallery-item">
  <img src="img/your-image.jpg" alt="Description" class="glitch-img-subtle">
  <p>Caption for your image</p>
</div>
```

### SoundCloud Embed (if you prefer)
1. Get your track's embed code from SoundCloud
2. Replace the HTML5 audio element with:
```html
<iframe width="100%" height="166" scrolling="no" frameborder="no" 
  allow="autoplay" 
  src="https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=YOUR_TRACK_URL">
</iframe>
```

## 🚀 Deployment

Since you're already using GitHub Pages:

1. Replace the existing files in your repository
2. Add your images to the `/img` folder
3. Add your audio files to the `/media` folder
4. Commit and push to GitHub
5. Your site will automatically update at `https://matildarosevin.github.io/MatildaStokesWebsite`

## 🖼️ Image Recommendations

### Sizes for best performance:
- Hero images: 1200-1600px wide
- Gallery images: 800-1000px wide
- Profile photo: 600px wide
- Keep file sizes under 500KB when possible (use JPG at 80-85% quality)

### What photos to include:
- **Granular synth page**: Close-ups of ceramic surfaces, sensors, full instrument shots, detail shots, you interacting with it
- **About page**: Professional headshot, studio shots, performance photos, ceramic work in progress
- **Other projects**: Cover images, process shots, relevant visuals

## 🔧 Customization

### Changing Colors
Edit the `:root` variables in `style.css`:
```css
:root{
  --accent:#ff4081;   /* Change this for different accent color */
  --accent2:#3b82f6;  /* Secondary accent */
}
```

### Adjusting Glitch Intensity
To make glitches more intense, find these sections in style.css and increase the values:
- `.glitch-text:hover` - increase transform values
- `.glitch-img-shift` - increase translate values
- `.glitch-text-hover::after` - increase opacity and text-shadow values

## 📱 Mobile Responsive
The site is fully responsive and will work well on phones and tablets. No additional work needed!

## ❓ Questions?
All the placeholder content is clearly marked with `<!-- TODO: -->` comments. Just search for "TODO" in each file to find what needs updating.
